Description:
    Explain the generator

Example:
    rails generate scss_class new_scss_class_name

    This will create:
        A new SCSS class. More precisely, it will generate a directory called
        new_scss_class_name in app/assets/stylesheets/project_specific. This
        directory will contain the files new_scss_class_name.scss and
        new_scss_class_name_defs.scss.
        
        See StylesheetWorkflowAndGuidelines documentation
        (http://www.ualberta.ca/~morrill/doc/StylesheetWorkflowAndGuidelines#)
        for more information.
